name: Bobbing for Apples Halloween 2021
description:
Hey, some of the other family members got together for a Halloween party last night and sent over this snap shot of bobbing for apples.   Looks like good, yummy fun!

Going to mint this one for #HENHalloween as well, will be dropped after the event officially starts.  #HENhalloween is hosted by @rblbab @cemo, @brainksy with tech and tools by @NFTbiker.  Hope you join in the fun!
